WEBVTT

00:00:00.384 --> 00:00:02.248
One of the possible symptoms of

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:04.648
lung cancer is shortness of breath.

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:06.056
When you inhale,

00:00:06.050 --> 00:00:08.464
the air moves down your main airway,

00:00:08.460 --> 00:00:09.984
called your trachea.

00:00:10.168 --> 00:00:12.888
The air then moves into smaller airways

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:14.920
that branch into your lungs. 

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.816
These smaller airways end in flexible

00:00:17.810 --> 00:00:21.072
elastic sacs that expand and contract

00:00:21.070 --> 00:00:22.784
as you breathe in and out,

00:00:22.780 --> 00:00:25.392
filling and emptying your lungs.

00:00:25.544 --> 00:00:28.080
Cancer is caused by cells that multiply

00:00:28.080 --> 00:00:31.352
faster than normal and, unlike normal cells,

00:00:31.350 --> 00:00:33.744
