00:00:33.740 --> 00:00:35.912
 All these cells growing together

00:00:35.910 --> 00:00:39.432
in one spot forms a mass or tumor.

00:00:39.560 --> 00:00:41.112
If not caught early,

00:00:41.152 --> 00:00:43.528
a mass in your lungs can grow large enough

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:44.992
to block flow of air

00:00:44.990 --> 00:00:47.872
in and out of the airways and sacs.

00:00:47.870 --> 00:00:50.600
Eventually, the area that cannot receive

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:52.448
air may collapse.

